      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中东紧张局势和 OPEC 关注，油价五连涨终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续五天上涨后下跌，中东冲突可能升级，但国际能源署预计，如果 OPEC+ 在下个季度按计划增加产量，将会出现盈余，从而抵消油价上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 23:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市因中东风险和美国数据而波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待美国价格数据来指导美联储的政策路径，同时中东紧张局势加剧打压了风险偏好，欧洲股市走势艰难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 22:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
